{
  "texts": [
    "It is important to be aware of the performance of different models.",
    "Scholars have compared models that vary in size, training data, and architecture to understand the capabilities and limitations of these models (Chae & Davidson, 2023).",
    "What they find is that there are tradeoffs between models depending on the research question and the resources available.",
    "For the kinds of coding tasks we outline in this paper, LLMs with accessible user interfaces are an optimal solution because of their relatively low cost and barrier to entry.",
    "How should the results be interpreted?"
  ]
}